OL,3,CNHS Wales app now allows patients to
OL,4,Ctrack their waiting list place
OL,6,FPeople in Wales can now track their
OL,7,Fplace on NHS waiting lists following
OL,8,Fan update on the NHS Wales app.
OL,10,FThe latest update allows people who
OL,11,Fhave been added to a waiting list
OL,12,Fsince December check their waiting
OL,13,Flist status, view their referral into
OL,14,Fhospital care, and access information
OL,15,Fto help manage their health while
OL,16,Fwaiting for treatment.
OL,18,FThey can also see details about
OL,19,Fupcoming hospital appointments,
OL,20,Fincluding directions and supporting
OL,21,Finformation.
