OL,3,CNHS Wales app now allows patients to
OL,4,Ctrack their waiting list place
OL,6,FIt comes as the latest data revealed
OL,7,Fthere were around just over 781,200
OL,8,Ftreatments waiting to be completed
OL,9,Fduring October 2025 - a drop of around
OL,10,F9,200 treatments from September.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government said that more
OL,13,Fthan 80,000 waiting list referrals and
OL,14,Fmore than 197,000 hospital appointment
OL,15,Fnotifications have been added to the
OL,16,Fapp so far.
