OL,3,CNHS Wales app now allows patients to
OL,4,Ctrack their waiting list place
OL,6,FMore than 650,000 people have
OL,7,Fregistered to use the bilingual NHS
OL,8,FWales App since it launched in April
OL,9,F2023 ` equivalent to one in five
OL,10,Fadults in Wales. There have also been
OL,11,Fnearly 13.5 million logins to the app
OL,12,Fand more than 3 million repeat
OL,13,Fprescription orders.
OL,15,FThe bilingual app aims to improve
OL,16,Faccess to healthcare services for
OL,17,Fpeople registered with a GP in Wales
OL,18,Fand is a part of the Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment's digital transformation
OL,20,Fstrategy for healthcare.
