OL,3,CNHS Wales app now allows patients to
OL,4,Ctrack their waiting list place
OL,6,FPeople can already order repeat
OL,7,Fprescriptions, view their health
OL,8,Ftimeline and prescription history,
OL,9,Fcheck their organ donation consent,
OL,10,Fand access health advice including
OL,11,Fscreening and wellbeing services.
OL,13,FThe app also lets people send secure
OL,14,Fmessages to their GP surgery and
OL,15,Fverify their identity using the Welsh
OL,16,FIdentity Verification Service, which
OL,17,Fhelps those unable to use the standard
OL,18,FNHS login.
