OL,3,CNHS Wales app now allows patients to
OL,4,Ctrack their waiting list place
OL,6,FMinister for Mental Health and
OL,7,FWellbeing Sarah Murphy said: "Our
OL,8,Fambition remains for the NHS Wales App
OL,9,Fto become the digital front door for
OL,10,Fall NHS and social care services.
OL,12,F"We promised to give people more
OL,13,Finformation about how long they can
OL,14,Fexpect to wait for treatment. These
OL,15,Fupdates deliver on that commitment.
OL,17,F"We will continue to update and expand
OL,18,Fthe app's capabilities, ensuring it
OL,19,Fmeets the needs of patients and
OL,20,Fclinicians alike.
